msgstr "Wolfenstein 3D"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:150
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_halflife.html.heex:113
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm.html.heex:179
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein_3d.html.heex:109
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Wolfenstein 3D (Arcade)"
msgstr "Wolfenstein 3D (Arcade)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein.html.heex:84
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein_3d.html.heex:94
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Wolfenstein 3D used raycasting (not true 3D) — all walls are the same height"
" and floors are flat. The 3D effect is an optical illusion."
msgstr ""
"Wolfenstein 3D usato raycasting (non vero 3D) — tutte le pareti sono la "
"stessa altezza e i pavimenti sono pianeggianti. L'effetto 3D è un'illusione "
"ottica."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:35
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein.html.heex:12
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Wolfenstein 3D: Escape from Castle"
msgstr "Wolfenstein 3D: Fuga dal Castello"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:116
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_halflife.html.heex:23
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Xash3D-FWGS"
msgstr "Xash3D-FWGS"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_lure.html.heex:16
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"You play Diermot, a peasant who must free the village of Turnvale from the "
"sorceress Selena and her army of Skorl. The game reached #1 on the British "
"Gallup charts at the beginning of July 1992 and remained in the Top 20 for "
"most of the year. Released as freeware on April 1, 2003. Runs on ScummVM "
"compiled to WebAssembly."
msgstr ""
"Si gioca Diermot, un contadino che deve liberare il villaggio di Turnvale "
"dalla strega Selena e il suo esercito di Skorl. Il gioco raggiunse <ph0> "
"</ph0> sulle classifiche British Gallup all'inizio di luglio 1992 e rimase "
"nella Top 20 per la maggior parte dell'anno. Rilasciato come freeware il 1 "
"aprile 2003. Corre su ScummVM compilato su WebAssembly."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade.html.heex:9
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "and type:"
msgstr "e tipo:"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_doom_shareware.html.heex:100
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"id Software estimated only 1% of shareware downloaders bought the full game "
"— yet this generated $100,000 per day in initial revenue, selling in one day"
" what Wolfenstein 3D had sold in one month."
msgstr ""
"id Software stimato solo l'1% dei downloader shareware ha acquistato il "
"gioco completo — tuttavia questo ha generato $100,000 al giorno in entrate "
"iniziali, vendendo in un giorno ciò che Wolfenstein 3D aveva venduto in un "
"mese."

