" infighting."
msgstr ""
"— Tutti i trucchi di movimento funzionano — strafe-running, caccia segreta e"
" infighting mostro."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake2_shareware.html.heex:44
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Alt-fire"
msgstr "— Alt-fire"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein.html.heex:61
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Ammo is shared across all bullet weapons. The chaingun is devastating but "
"burns ammo fast."
msgstr ""
"— Le munizioni sono condivise su tutte le armi da fuoco. Il chaingun è "
"devastante ma brucia le munizioni velocemente."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein.html.heex:75
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein_3d.html.heex:72
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Blue-uniformed SS guards deal heavy damage and move fast. Take them out "
"first."
msgstr ""
"— Le guardie SS uniformate blu danneggiano pesantemente e si muovono "
"velocemente. Portali fuori prima."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_halflife.html.heex:54
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Break every crate you see. They often contain health kits, ammo, and "
"batteries."
msgstr ""
"- Rompi ogni cassa che vedi. Spesso contengono kit per la salute, munizioni "
"e batterie."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_librequake.html.heex:62
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Bunny hopping and strafe jumping work just like in original Quake."
msgstr ""
"— Bunny hopping e strafe jumping lavoro proprio come in Quake originale."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_drascula.html.heex:53
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Cartoon comedy logic applies. Absurd combinations often work."
msgstr ""
"— Si applica la logica della commedia del cartone. Le combinazioni assunte "
"spesso funzionano."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_lure.html.heex:53
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Characters follow their own routines. If someone isn't where you expect, "
"wait or check elsewhere."
msgstr ""
"— I caratteri seguono le proprie routine. Se qualcuno non è dove ti aspetti,"
" aspetta o controlla altrove."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_drascula.html.heex:57
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Characters have extensive conversation trees with hilarious lines."
msgstr ""
"— I caratteri hanno ampi alberi di conversazione con linee esilatrici."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_doom.html.heex:99
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Circle-strafing around enemies is the fundamental DOOM skill. Never stand "
"still."
msgstr ""
"— Il cerchio-strafing intorno ai nemici è l'abilità DOOM fondamentale. Mai "
"stare fermo."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein_3d.html.heex:79
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Collecting treasure counts toward your score. Hunt for hidden treasure "
"rooms."
msgstr ""
"— Raccogliere tesori conta verso il tuo punteggio. Caccia per i tesori "
"nascosti."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_bass.html.heex:36
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Combine inventory items"
msgstr "— Combinare gli elementi di inventario"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm.html.heex:88
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Combine or use inventory items"
msgstr "— Combinare o utilizzare oggetti di inventario"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_librequake.html.heex:55
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
