msgid "— Walk / interact with object"
msgstr "— Camminare / interagire con l'oggetto"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_doom.html.heex:113
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Walls with different textures often hide secret rooms with weapons and "
"ammo. Press Use on everything."
msgstr ""
"— Mura con texture diverse spesso nascondono stanze segrete con armi e "
"munizioni. Premere Usa su tutto."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_halflife_uplink.html.heex:55
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Weapon category"
msgstr "— Categoria di armamento"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_doom.html.heex:86
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake.html.heex:45
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake2.html.heex:39
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein.html.heex:41
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Weapon select"
msgstr "— Selezione dell'arma"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_halflife_uplink.html.heex:64
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Weapons have alt-fire modes. The shotgun's double-barrel blast is "
"devastating up close."
msgstr ""
"— Le armi hanno modalità alt-fire. L'esplosione a doppio barile del fucile "
"sta devastando da vicino."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_hacx.html.heex:63
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Weapons look and behave differently from classic DOOM. Learn their quirks."
msgstr ""
"— Le armi sembrano e si comportano in modo diverso dal classico DOOM. Impara"
" le loro quirk."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_freedoom2.html.heex:77
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Works with community DOOM II mods — decades of free content at your "
"fingertips."
msgstr ""
"— Funziona con la comunità mod DOOM II — decenni di contenuto libero a "
"portata di mano."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake2.html.heex:23
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Yamagi Quake II compiled to WebAssembly via Emscripten. Features WebGL 2 "
"rendering, software rendering fallback, and in-browser save games."
msgstr ""
"— Yamagi Quake II compilato su WebAssembly tramite Emscripten. "
"Caratteristiche WebGL 2 rendering, software di rendering fallback, e in-"
"browser salvare giochi."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_wolfenstein_3d.html.heex:58
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— You can hear guards through doors. Plan your approach before opening."
msgstr ""
"- Potete sentire le guardie attraverso le porte. Pianifica il tuo approccio "
"prima di aprire."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_dreamweb.html.heex:60
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— You can only carry a limited number of items. Choose wisely what to take."
msgstr ""
"— È possibile trasportare solo un numero limitato di elementi. Scegli con "
"saggezza cosa prendere."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake2_shareware.html.heex:63
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— You'll revisit areas with new keys and equipment. Remember the layout."
msgstr ""
"— Rivisiterete le aree con nuove chiavi e attrezzature. Ricorda il layout."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm_lure.html.heex:67
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Your companion Ratpouch can perform unique actions. Tell him to do things."
msgstr ""
"— Il tuo compagno Ratpouch può eseguire azioni uniche. Digli di fare le "
"cose."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_quake2.html.heex:52
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Your starting Blaster has infinite ammo but low damage. Switch to better "
"weapons as soon as you find them."
msgstr ""
"— Il tuo primo Blaster ha munizioni infinite ma danni bassi. Passa a armi "
"migliori non appena li trovi."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_halflife.html.heex:24
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— an open-source reimplementation of the GoldSource engine, compiled to "
"WebAssembly via Emscripten (GPL-2.0). Features WebGL2 rendering and Web "
"Audio support."
msgstr ""
"— una riattuazione open source del motore GoldSource, compilato su "
"WebAssembly tramite Emscripten (GPL-2.0). Rendering WebGL2 e supporto Web "
"Audio."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_arcade_scummvm.html.heex:68
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— the legendary multi-engine adventure game interpreter with an official "
"Emscripten backend, compiled to WebAssembly (GPL-3.0). Game data is loaded "
"on-demand via HTTP filesystem."
msgstr ""
"— il leggendario interprete di gioco di avventura multi-motore con un "
"backend ufficiale Emscripten, compilato su WebAssembly (GPL-3.0). I dati del"
" gioco vengono caricati on-demand tramite filesystem HTTP."
